      "B": "full dominant cycle bridge D7-G7-C7-F7 (V/V/V-V/V/-V/-V)",
      "A1": "I with dominant cycle, briefly tonicizes II (D) via A7 then Bb7 pivots back",
      "C": "IV-I motion (Eb-Bb7-Eb-Ebm) then I-#io7-ii-V7-I final cadence"
    },
